                            <comment id="13864620" author="thejas" created="Tue, 7 Jan 2014 19:58:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good. A nit - I think it would be bit more easier to read this way -&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (e &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; HiveSQLException) {
       &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; ((HiveSQLException)e).toTStatus();
     }
    TStatus tStatus = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; TStatus(TStatusCode.ERROR_STATUS);
    tStatus.setErrorMessage(e.getMessage());
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; tStatus;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
